<div class="col-12 col-xl-4">
    <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-header pb-0 p-3">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-8 d-flex align-items-center">
                    <h6 class="mb-0">Profil Bilgileri</h6>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body p-3">
            <p class="text-sm">
                Traversal üye sistemine hoşgeldiniz. Sol tarafta yer alan menüden yeni rezervasyon oluşturabilmekle beraber geçmiş, aktif ve onaylanmayan rezervasyonlarınızı görüntüleyebilirsiniz.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-group profile-info-list">
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 text-sm">
                    <strong class="text-dark">Kullanıcı Adı: </strong><span>@ViewBag.mUsername</span>
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 text-sm">
                    <strong class="text-dark">Ad Soyad: </strong><span>@ViewBag.mNameSurname</span>
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 text-sm">
                    <strong class="text-dark">Telefon No: </strong><span>@ViewBag.mPhoneNumber</span>
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item border-0 ps-0 text-sm">
                    <strong class="text-dark">E-posta: </strong><span class="email-ellipsis">@ViewBag.mEmail</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<style>
    .profile-info-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

        .profile-info-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .profile-info-list strong {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .profile-info-list span {
            flex: 2;
            text-align: right; 
            overflow: hidden;
            white-space: nowrap;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

    .email-ellipsis {
        max-width: 200px; 
    }

</style>